<plot>Angel, a young Hispanic man experiencing romantic woes (Arias), tries to defraud his way to financial gain by swiping credit cards at a gas station, but is caught in the act by the leader of a gang of home invaders (David) who forces him to chose - to join the crew of depraved burglars in their pursuit of trespass, or face uncertain reprisal. For a time it seems that Angel was born for this life of crime, but the gang's transgressions continue to devolve until the inevitable disaster brings about their unraveling, leaving Angel to chose where his loyalties lie - between his fellow gangsters and his own destiny as a prison-bound felon. On the all-too-short road from urban minority to wannabe gangster, will Angel learn fast enough - the life-lessons that just may help him save his own fate?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?243910</url></doc>
